. Get rid of hosts/. Instead, each machine will have its own script that runs
  the generic makefile and then copies in its own specific extensions.
. Get rid of make-links.sh. The generic makefile should do this stuff.
. Resolve detect-display.sh. We should make the is_connected function a
  standard script in bin, and then per-machine configurations can just
  use it to choose the right xrandr script to run.
